strings: <voice_0x01001417>That's all I can do. No one can walk into the ham unnoticed.
<voice_0x01001418>But the mountains are full of caves. You should be able to make it to the top of the hill.
<voice_0x01001419>If you want to return to the mountains, call me and I'll take you home.
<voice_0x0100141A>Until we meet again. Hold my ball, you are my only hope
